{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could not be open and sincere talking to people because if I would take a side of Jews and-- or a-- and-- and-- and express myself against these massacres, the Holocaust and so on, then right away, they say, oh, because you are Jew.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a lot of conflicts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a lot of-- even here in Canada.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Imagine, when I was working with-- with Canadian Marconi, I had no car at that time, in the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, the people, they introduce me to one of Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, there was a former Polish officer who was at Canadian Marconi working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was living not far from that place what we were living in Tremont.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was coming to pick me up to go to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we were driving, we were driving through the lower of Tremont.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the lower of Tremont, there is a lot of Jewish people living there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there the-- the-- the Jewish boys were playing on the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was swearing always to me, swearing on those boys that they are interfering with his driving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and once he said, too bad that Hitler was not in Canada that he could get rid of these Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Terrible, right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did tell him that my wife is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one day-- but when I was working for Canadian-- for RCA, I was so naive because I didn't know that the people, Polish people living in Canada, they could be free, free from all this prejudice.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- there was another Polish colleague, engineer, working with the RCA.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she-- and I-- I told him that my wife is Jewish, and we came, and I came with a Jewish wife.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
